column2: "Planet Harukotan has calmed down all thanks to the Ashen Miko, Sukunahime's appearance."
"Well, the previous status quo was due to her slumbering and not doing anything in the first place..."
"For now, let's do our best in what we can do."
"There's something we can do?"
"The recently discovered area on Planet Vopar, the Facility, needs to be investigated."
"I hope to salvage some of Luther's research data and records through an in-depth investigation."
"There might be some useful data being left to rot. We might even find some data regarding Dark Falz [Double]."
"I got it. Leave this to me."
"Hold right up, Matoi."
"C-can I help you, Sara?"
"Matoi, you've been skipping out on your checkups, haven't you?"
"Gulp!"
"I thought so. I thought it was strange that there weren't any new status updates lately."
"W-why did Sara look into my status reports?"
"That's not important. What's important is you going to Philia now and getting your inspections done."

"Oh, and don't forget about
Clarissa's maintenance."
"B-both Clarissa and I are fine. We're still going fine--"
"Uu... I'm sorry. I understand... I'll be going now."
"Geez. She needs to take better care of both her weapon and body."

"You're surprisingly worried about Matoi aren't you, Sara? Usually you would've said \"This has nothing to do with me!\" or something along that
line. Heheh!"
"I don't want to hear that from you! You're the one who's supposed to be monitoring Matoi's condition."
"Besides, there's no way I would say something like that."

"
Obtained Matterboard [Recollection of Conception].
"
